data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 2-bedroom plus den waterfront condo, where breathtaking south-facing views of the Halifax River await you. Step inside to discover a tastefully designed home adorned with luxury vinyl flooring throughout, adding a touch of elegance to every corner. The modern kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, creating a perfect setting for culinary delights. Enjoy the tranquility of the water view balcony, offering a serene space to unwind and soak in the picturesque scenery. Convenience meets style with a walk-in laundry room, providing ample storage for all your needs. The community amenities are equally impressive, featuring an outdoor heated pool, in-ground spa, BBQ area, dock, gym, and club house. Plus, you'll have the added convenience of an assigned parking space in the garage and extra storage just down the hall. Don't miss the opportunity to experience luxury living in this gated waterfront paradise. Come and make this remarkable condo your own!
